const StageStepView = ({stageFinished, stageLbl, stageDesc}) => {
  return (
    <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", borderWidth: 2 }}>
      <Text
        style={{
          fontFamily: "archivo-600",
          color: "rgba(255,255,255,1)",
          fontSize: 30,
        }}
      >
        1
      </Text>
      <View style={styles.subscription1StackStack}>
        <View style={{ flexDirection: "row" }}>
          <Text
            style={{
              fontFamily: "archivo-600",
              color: "rgba(255,255,255,1)",
              fontSize: 25,
              marginRight: 25,
              opacity: stageFinished ? 1 : 0.5,
            }}
          >
            {stag}
          </Text>
          {stageFinished && (
            <View style={styles.stageChecked}>
              <EntypoIcon name="check" style={styles.checkedIcon} />
            </View>
          )}
        </View>
        <Text
          style={{
            fontFamily: "archivo-500",
            color: "rgba(155,155,155,1)",
            fontSize: 23,
            opacity: stageFinished ? 1 : 0.5,
          }}
        >
          PLAN INFO
        </Text>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
};
